longBusinessSummary: Diamond Fields Resources Inc. explores for and evaluates mineral properties worldwide. The company explores for diamonds, zinc, copper, silver, gold, lead, zircon, and other metals. It holds a 100% interest in the Namibian Diamond project; and Madagascar Zircon project. The company was formerly known as Diamond Fields International Ltd. and changed its name to Diamond Fields Resources Inc. in December 2017. The company incorporated in 2000 and is based in Vancouver, Canada. Diamond Fields Resources Inc. is a subsidiary of Spirit Resources SARL.
